<lyrics>[V1]
 1-rby kẖyrk wrḥmh ytbʿạny fy ạlṭryq
 flhdẖạ lst ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ ạ̉y ʿwz ạ̉y ḍyq
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉rfʿ qlby ạ̹lyk wạ̉gẖny fy ạlḥyạh ạ̉nt kẖyry wạ̹lhy wkẖlạṣy wạlnjạh
 2-tsmʿny kl ywm ṣwtk ạlḥạny ạlrqyq
 fy ḥdytẖ ysby qlby yʿṭny ạ̉mnạaⁿ wtẖyq
 3-ạ̉nt tṣgẖy bạ̹htmạm fy ạ̉nyny wạlậlậm
 wtzyl kl kẖwf tmlạ̉ny bạlslạm
 4-ạ̉wdʿ ʿmry ldyk yạ rfyqy fy ạlmsyr
 lys ly kẖl ạ̉myn mtẖlk mʿy ysyr</lyrics>
<title>rby kẖyrk</title>
</song>